USAGE

1. Extract reviews from Flipkart :: review_crawler_flipkart.py
This script fetches the defined no. of reviews for a flipkart product starting from page 1 to page N (each review page in flipkart consists of 10 reviews).
The script stores 3 components for each review: (i) Title; (ii) Complete text; (iii) Rating given by user.

2. Find the sentiment of each review using various Sentiment APIs :: process_reviews.py
This script runs sentiment analyzer of AlchemyAPI, AYLIEN and Textalytics API on each review and stores the result
as POSITIVE or NEGATIVE.

3. Benchmark the results of each API: benchmark.py
This script compares the results of each API and outputs the accuracy.